      "content": "Wait, \"treasure hunt\"? That's a weird way to put it. I just need the actual math for the calculations. Can you show me the specific formula used to get those percentages, and also explain the \"half-year convention\" part of MACRS? I need to make sure I'm calculating the first year's deduction correctly.",
